Band select

Demand purpose:

 In order to quickly set up any frequency band of mode that the machine supported to improve the test efficiency. 

*******************************

Function description:

 1)Read All the bands and modes from NV. 

 2)Distinguish SIM1 and SIM2

******************************* 

Implementation scheme :

 1)Judge the card slot of SIM card, how many card slot show appropriate SIM 
 2)The display interface will provide frequency options for each model 3)Use the AT commands to select the frequency band, such as setting up AT:AT+SBAND=1,12,38 in band38 under LTE; if the settings are successful, the corresponding information prompt box will be popped up.

CFU

Demand purpose:

 In order to quickly set up unconditional calling transfer to improve the test efficiency. 

*******************************

Function description:

 1)Provide three radio buttons:Default, Always Query, Always Not Query . 

 2)Configure Default: when the properties of the mobile 'persist.radio.ssda.mode' are tdd-csfb, fdd-csfb, and CSFB, the Default is Always Not Query in the option list, and the other Default is Always Query. 

 3)The relevant settings are written by the 'persist.sys.callforwarding attribute', and when the Always Query option is selected, the 'persist.sys.callforwarding' is written 1, namely, SystemProperties.set ("persist.sys.callforwarding", "1"); When selecting Always Not Query option, write 0 to 'persist.sys.callforwarding', SystemProperties.set("persist.sys.callforwarding", "0")

NetInfo Statistics

Demand purpose:

 In order to quickly Query route test information. 

*******************************

Function description:

 Show the route test informations:

 1)The number, success rate and average delay of cell reselection. 

 2)The number of cell handover, success rate and average delay

 3)Network time statistics .

 4)Statistics of the number of net loss 

******************************* 

Implementation scheme :

 1)'AT+SPENGMD=0,7,1' get the frequency and success rate of cell reselection. 
 2)'AT+SPENGMD=0,7,2' get the number and success rate of cell handover. 
 3)'AT+SPENGMD=0,7,7' get the time in 2G/3G/LTE. 
 4)'AT+SPENGMD=0,2,2' get the drop time in 2G/3G/LTE .

GPRS Test

Demand purpose:

 In order to quickly set Attach/Detach, Activate/Deactive PDP, and Send Gprs data for testing GPRS. 

*******************************

Function description:

For different SIM cards, do the following tests :

 1)'AT+CGATT' is used to attach or disattach GPRS services. 

 2)'AT+CGACT' is used to activate or inactivate PDP

 3)'AT+SGPRSDATA' is used to realized to send datas.

*******************************

Implementation scheme :

 There are two input box.

 The first input box is used to set the length of GPRS datas(1-16000) used to be send; 

 The second input box is used to set appointed GPRS data.

De-sense-PLL

Demand purpose:

 It is used to modify the register of PLL in engineer mode, like reading and writing ARM register in mobile tester. 

*******************************

Function description:

This function is actually a function of reading and writing the fixed address register, using the 'lookat' command, send 'lookat' command by 'cmd_skt' service: 

 1)Address is 8 bits and 4 bytes align address, 8 bits are controled by app, 4 bytes align address are controled by cmd_skt. 

 2)Number's default is 1, the input value is the parameters carried by 'look at -l'.

 3)Click Read button will send 'lookat –l num 0x addr', if the Return value contains 'VALUE' means read register successful, the return will show in result zone; otherwise, the fail reason will show in result zone.

 4)Click Write button will send 'lookat –s 0x data 0x addr', if the return value contains 'Result' means successful, otherwise means failed.

Demand purpose:

 Add the editing options of SMS center in the EngineerMode to make it convenient for laboratory testing. When the white card defaults to no SMS center, it can send SMS normally. 

*******************************

Function description:

 1).SMS center numbers of SIM cards can be displayed. If two SIM cards are inserted, they should be listed separately. The interfaces involved is:

 2).The SMS center number of SIM card can be modified. If two SIM cards are inserted, attention to paid to distinguishing. The interfaces involved is:

SmsManagerEx.getDefault().setSmscForSubscriber(smscAddr, subId);

Coulometer Power Test(2018-02-09)

Demand purpose:Users can see the approximate power consumption of a scene when using a mobile phone

*******************************

Implementation Method ：

1)When pressing START button, echo 1 > /sys/class/power_supply/sprdfgu/cc_test_cmd. 

2)When pressing END button, echo 0 > /sys/class/power_supply/sprdfgu/cc_test_cmd.
Read the datas from cat /sys/class/power_supply/sprdfgu/cc_test_result. 

*******************************

UI design:

 The data are recorded every 10 minutes. After the end, all data stored in every 10 minutes are plotted with a simple curve through the value of "vertical axis time" and "vertical axis power consumption". 
 Test long standby power, such as 24, 48 hours, can collect data every one or two hours, and then draw it for one point with each data.
 If the test time of the simple scene is less than 20 minutes, there is no need to draw a curve.

 There can not overlapping part of the test time for each time period.

Camera FPS(2018-03-01)

Demand purpose:

Easy adjustment of taking video \ preview frame rate and indirect debugging of camera power 

*******************************

Function description:
 Take video / preview frame indirect adjustment. Add a fixed frame rate function in the EngineerMode. Take video and preview can input the max and Minimum frame that you want.

*******************************

Implementation Method：

1)Preview frame rate settings ：
 setprop persist.sys.camera.preview.fps abcd //Setting the preview frame rate from cd to ab

2)Video frame rate setting ：
 setprop persist.sys.camera.record.fps abcd //Setting the video frame rate from cd to ab

3)Restore defaults
Avoid the default value not restored after the tester is completed a functional switch. One button restores all of the above functions and switches to default values .

 To set the frame rate to a certain value, the fixed video frame rate is 20fps as an example:
 setprop persist.sys.camera.record.fps 2020，can not write as setprop persist.sys.camera.record.fps 20，The first two bits of the parameter string are maxfps, and the next two bits are minfps, which can not be missing .user version can use *#*#83781#*#* -> HARDWARETEST -> Camera FPS。

*******************************

UI design:

 Camera FPS have three functions：
 1)Preview 
 2)Recording 
 3)Restore Defaults

SETH Network card GRO Converging function (2018-03-12)

Demand purpose:

 Make this function in EngineerMode, Convenient tester for manual opening test .

*******************************

Function description:
 SETH Network card GRO Converging function belong to AP side Network card downlink data message Converging function, can reduce the processing pressure of the kernel network subsystem, It also reduces the number of the uplink TCP ACK and reduces the MIPs overhead of CP .

*******************************

Implementation Method：

1)Open GRO, setprop ctl.start gro_on

2)Close GRO, setprop ctl.start gro_of

3)Query :sys/module/seth/parameter/gro_enable value is 1 to open gro，value is 0 to close gro。

*******************************

Acceptance plan :

 When downloading by FTP, Open GRO, capturing cap log of ap side , the downlink message will have the effect of gathering, and it can be judged from the length of the message, almost is bigger than 1500 bytes. close GRO, The downlink message length is about 1500 bytes

Ping packages Test(2018-03-26)

Demand purpose:

It is convenient for the IOT test to check whether the Ping packet chain is normal or not, and at present, the UE Ping server is carried out through the computer through the USB binding computer, which is not conducive to the operation of the testers. 

*******************************

Function description:

 It can be operated by the UE Ping server through the EngineerMode. IP type selection, Ping packet time, Ping packet interval, and Ping packet size can be carried out .

PDN Test(2018-03-26)

Demand purpose:

PDN is an essential operation in the IOT test, which is now set by the APK and AT commands, and the process is complex and is not conducive to the operation of the testers. 

*******************************

Function description:

 UE Attach established the first road to build the default carrying capacity, It can build multiple PDN through EngineerMode, each PDN corresponding to different APN parameters, to set up special carrying capacity and special carrying capacity, special bearing will activate and default carrying capacity associated, and can be activated to default and special carrying capacity.

Adb shell Test(2018-03-26)

Demand purpose:

 In order to facilitate the user to run the shell command directly on the phone, it provides the function of direct input to the shell command. 

*******************************

Function description:

 The interface can directly enter the shell command that you want to run in the edit box. Click start to run the command, and the results will be outputed directly under the command box, which can run two shell at the same time.

Frequency Point Test(2018-03-26)

Demand purpose:

For convenience of outfield testing, we need to input required frequency point, one key start lock function. 

*******************************

Function description:

 The method of locking LTE frequency point:

AT+SFUN=5
AT+SPCLEANINFO=4
AT+SPFRQ=0,4,earfcn //lock frequency point，earfcn is the number of frequency point which need to input
 AT+SFUN=4 

The method of unlocking LTE frequency point:

AT+SFUN=5
AT+SPFRQ=1
AT+SFUN=4

The method of locking WCDMA frequency point:

at+spfrq=0,0,earfcn//lock frequency point，earfcn is the number of frequency point which need to input
